➜蔡权生（广东）：《一盏烛光》
http://www.sohu.com/a/415974768_100115135	45989
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200901/64de91eaff9446faba98757ee750e209.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《一盏烛光》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/蔡权生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一盏烛光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">照亮多少思乡的情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">春来秋去 </p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在繁华的城市里踏上远航</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却又在落日中遥望故乡</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">往事随风扬起</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">岁月隐留厚厚的沧桑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一盏烛光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>或许是思念的执着</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>每当我举起烛光</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>随着微光顺着你的方向慢慢地步入迷茫的夜里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>水中的影子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>深深地映在我的眼眸里</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我的脑海里依然是你</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而你正如夜里的眼睛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>让前行的路上不再迷茫</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
